	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. pl. 43. See MRR 2.339. To App. BC 4.47, add a reference to Val. Max. 7.38, who preserves the praenomen. See Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 156-RP 2.605-606.[224]\n" ;
